### Authentication Tests

### Register User
POST http://user-management.local/api/v1/user-management/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_data": {
    "username": "test-user",
    "email": "test-user@example.com",
    "password": "Password123!",
    "full_name": "Test User",
    "bio": "A test test-user for development"
  }
}

###

### Login User (capture tokens)
POST http://user-management.local/api/v1/user-management/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test-user",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

> {%
// Save the access token and refresh token from the login response
client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.token.accessToken);
client.global.set("refreshToken", response.body.token.refreshToken);
%}

###

