### Refresh Token
POST http://user-management.local/api/v1/user-management/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###

### Request Password Reset
POST http://user-management.local/api/v1/user-management/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

###

### Confirm Password Reset (use token from logs)
POST http://user-management.local/api/v1/user-management/auth/reset-password/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reset_token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...",
  "new_password": "NewSecurePass123!"
}

###

### Logout User
POST http://user-management.local/api/v1/user-management/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

